Package: pal
Title: A color palette search engine.
Description: Search the color palette that best suit
    your interests can become a tired activity. 
    This package facilitates find your ideal color
    palette by making the package collections: cpt-city,
    hex-color and paletteer more accessible to realize 
    queries. There are more than 80 000 > palettes 
    waiting to be used!.
Version: 0.0.0.1
Author: Cesar Aybar
Maintainer: Cesar Aybar <csaybar@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/csaybar/pal/
BugReports: https://github.com/csaybar/pal/issues
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Depends:
    R (>= 3.4)
